{"tid":314034,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"大家有無奇怪強迫症(OCD)行為？","createTime":"2017-07-08T22:49:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-10T02:35:18.000Z","uid":68457,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2aef850667d9fccfced3960efec3ec0b411b9caf","tid":314034,"uid":68457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T22:49:29.000Z","msg":"我幾乎每晚臨訓著前會專登出廳檢查有無熄冷氣/風扇<br />\n明知已經熄左<br />\n<br />\n又例如出門口等𨋢，會衝返入屋檢查有無熄煤氣爐（有時）<br />\n根本無煮過食<br />\n<br />\n又外出無耐好焦慮係咪唔記得閂門，癡線 （有時）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實駛唔駛睇醫生？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"064335bc3ab7480e7b6c87260215a8ceb7717ff5","tid":314034,"uid":76117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T22:51:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1c69e5ecb7a15c8a80674f6172dd98f8781190c3","tid":314034,"uid":8810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T00:00:28.000Z","msg":"個個人都有啲，冇乜大不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8f7c5b37763d08bad6b47fe479b43501a63d80e","tid":314034,"uid":68457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T04:38:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個個人都有啲，冇乜大不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都唔知係咪要去到焦慮症嘅程度先要睇醫生<br />\n有時落左街擔心無鎖好門窗個心囉囉孿"},{"pid":"ba6d21a15859ee04f0435481e2d905e00cd702fa","tid":314034,"uid":55922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T05:04:59.000Z","msg":"成日洗手，上堂拍卡拍 N 次 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/12.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6233de2407091609dce6f1918d102c1b6d3e8d61","tid":314034,"uid":61798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T05:18:07.000Z","msg":"未夠啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n未去到真係影響日常生活都未算<br />\n<br />\n我自己每日都要剪幾次指甲，剪到入肉都要剪<br /